/0c2b8/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 207w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/0dbe3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 414w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/deba3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 827w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/35099/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 1241w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/7f9aa/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 1654w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/bb9a8/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" src=\"/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/deba3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"Woman reading book with cup of coffee\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/0c2b8/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 207w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/0dbe3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 414w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/deba3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 827w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/35099/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 1241w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/7f9aa/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 1654w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/bb9a8/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 827px) 100vw, 827px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 827px) 100vw, 827px\" srcset=\"/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/0c2b8/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 207w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/0dbe3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 414w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/deba3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 827w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/35099/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 1241w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/7f9aa/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 1654w,\n/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/bb9a8/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" src=\"/static/46ec4166d5d3115d793c64b601d4e63f/deba3/national-read-a-book-day-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"Woman reading book with cup of coffee\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>If you like to escape into a world of fiction and fantasy, we recommend:</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Lightning-Thief-Percy-Jackson-Olympians/dp/0786838655/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647505&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=lightning+thief\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lightning Thief</a> – Rick Riordan<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Harry-Potter-Sorcerers-Stone-Rowling/dp/059035342X/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647574&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=harry+potter+book\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Harry Potter</a> – JK Rowling<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Enders-Ender-Quintet-Orson-Scott/dp/0812550706/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647607&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=ender%27s+game\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ender’s Game</a> – Orson Scott Card<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/War-Worlds-H-G-Wells/dp/1546517529/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647645&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=war+of+the+worlds\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">War of the Worlds</a> &#8211; H. G. Wells<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Hobbit-J-R-Tolkien/dp/054792822X/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647661&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=the+hobbit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> The Hobbit</a> &#8211; J.R.R. Tolkien<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Far-Blue-Mountains-Sacketts/dp/0553276883/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647683&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=To+the+Far+Blue+Mountains+-+Louis+L%E2%80%99Amour\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">To the Far Blue Mountains</a> &#8211; Louis L’Amour<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>If you want something more down to earth and pertinent to everyday life, try these non-fiction and self-help titles:</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Dont-Sweat-Small-Stuff-Its/dp/0786881852/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647704&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=Don%E2%80%99t+Sweat+the+Small+Stuff+%E2%80%93+Richard+Carlson\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Don’t Sweat the Small Stuff</a> – Richard Carlson<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Last-Lecture-Randy-Pausch/dp/1401323251/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647727&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=The+Last+Lecture+%E2%80%93+Jeffrey+Zaslow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Last Lecture</a> – Jeffrey Zaslow<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Rich-Sharon-Lechter-Robert-Kiyosaki/dp/B007CIHXFS/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647757&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=Rich+Dad%2C+Poor+Dad+-+Robert+Kiyosaki+and+Sharon+Lechter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rich Dad, Poor Dad</a> &#8211; Robert Kiyosaki and Sharon Lechter<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Richest-Babylon-Clason-George-Samuel/dp/1530439027/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647773&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=The+Richest+Man+in+Babylon+-+George+Samuel+Clason\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Richest Man in Babylon</a> &#8211; George Samuel Clason<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Millionaire-Next-Door-Surprising-Americas/dp/1589795474/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647806&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=The+Millionaire+Next+Door+-+Thomas+J.+Stanley\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Millionaire Next Door</a> &#8211; Thomas J. Stanley<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>If you are hungry for some more marketing wisdom and advertising prowess, check out:</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Confessions-Advertising-Man-David-Ogilvy/dp/190491537X/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647841&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=Confessions+of+an+Advertising+Man+%E2%80%93+David+Ogilvy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Confessions of an Advertising Man</a> – David Ogilvy<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Tipping-Point-Little-Things-Difference/dp/0316346624/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647858&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=The+Tipping+Point+%E2%80%93+Malcolm+Gladwell\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Tipping Point</a> – Malcolm Gladwell<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Buyology-Truth-Lies-About-Why/dp/0385523890/ref=sr_1_fkmr0_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647879&amp;sr=1-1-fkmr0&amp;keywords=Buyology%3A+Truth+and+Lies+About+What+We+Buy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Buyology: Truth and Lies About What We Buy</a> &#8211; Martin Lindstrom<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Copywriters-Handbook-Step-Step-Writing/dp/0805078045/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1504647924&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=The+Copywriter%E2%80%99s+Handbook+%E2%80%93+Robert+W.+Bly\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Copywriter’s Handbook</a> – Robert W. Bly<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nWhatever you’re in the mood for, we have plenty of page-turners to choose from. Happy reading!<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&#8211; The PM Group<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About The PM Group</a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journa</em>l. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, nonprofit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area nonprofit organizations in the last 15 years! It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"Helping You Get a Read on Our Agency","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Helping You Get a Read on Our Agency","url":"/helping-get-read-agency/"}],"title":"Helping You Get a Read on Our Agency | The PM Group","metaDesc":"In honor of National Read a Book Day, we are sharing some of The PM Group’s favorite books...","focuskw":"Book Day","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Helping You Get a Read on Our Agency | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"In honor of National Read a Book Day, we are sharing some of The PM Group’s favorite books...","opengraphImage":{"altText":"Woman reading a book in bed and holding a cup of coffee","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1-2048x2048.jpg 2048w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/national-read-a-book-day-square-scaled-1-1568x1568.jpg 1568w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/helping-get-read-agency/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/